title: Science
text:
To obtain my University Diploma of Technology in Organic and Synthesis Chemistry at the Université Paris-Est Créteil, I had the opportunity to do a 3 month internship in Recife, Brazil at th Universidade Federale de Pernambouco in Departement of Fundamental Chemistry under Marcello Navarro’s tutoring. This is a poster I made for my internship in Brazil, in the Universidade Federal de Pernambouco (Recife).
